<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #1e3a8a;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .credentials {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        .credential-item {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1e3a8a;
            display: inline-block;
            width: 100px;
        }
        .button {
            background-color: #1e3a8a;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to OTIC Workforce!</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello <strong>{{ user.first_name }} {{ user.last_name }}</strong>,</p>
        
        <p>Your account has been created successfully. You can now access the OTIC Workforce platform with the following credentials:</p>
        
        <div class="credentials">
            <div class="credential-item">
                <span class="label">Username:</span>
                <strong>{{ user.username }}</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="credential-item">
                <span class="label">Email:</span>
                <strong>{{ user.email }}</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="credential-item">
                <span class="label">Password:</span>
                <strong>{{ password }}</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="credential-item">
                <span class="label">Role:</span>
                <strong>{{ role|title }}</strong>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <p>For security reasons, we recommend changing your password after your first login.</p>
        
        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{ login_url }}" class="button">Login to OTIC Workforce</a>
        </div>
        
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact your administrator.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2026 OTIC Workforce. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>